name: Point Stacking Ring
description: Handmade, shaped and polished point stacking ring! Great for wearing with other rings!

name: Rib Necklace
description: 4 1/2" of planished, hammered and polished collar pendant that sits right below your collar bones. Necklace length is 18".

name: Baby Cuff/Chain Ring
description: Handmade, hammered, polished and slightly adjustable ring. The band measures approx 1/4" wide and the chain is 1/2" in length.

name: Hammered Double Twist Ring
description:
Handshaped, hammered and polished double twist ring that can be worn many ways --

X facing up
X facing down
X facing sideways


Small - Size 5-6
Medium - Size 7-8

name: Choupette Kitten Ring
description:
Pick your metal - 14k Gold Fill or Sterling Silver

Handmade and polished kitten ring!

name: Raw Pyrite Stone Ring
description:
A delicate, hand wrapped 14k gold fill ring with a raw pyrite stone measuring approx 3/8".

**All stones are unique and have their own shape and shine..

name: Hammered Bar Studs
description: Approx 1/2" hammered, filed and polished 14k gold fill or sterling silver bars on sterling silver posts and backs.

name: Black Grey Druzy Ring
description: Raw, sparkling, black-grey druzy, measuring approx 8mm in a hammered, four prong setting with pointed claws on a faceted 14k gold fill hammered band.

name: Gold Brass Heart Studs
description: Mini gold brass heart charms measuring 1/4" on sterling silver posts.

name: Gold Brass Lightning Bolt Studs
description: Gold tone brass lightning bolt charms measuring about 1/4" on sterling silver posts and backs.

name: Green Peridot Ring
description: Raw, bright green peridot stone set in a handmade four prong claw setting on a hammered 14k gold fill band.

name: Sterling Silver "V" Necklace
description: Handmade, shaped and polished "V" pendant with a round hammered texture. "V" measures 2 1/2" wide x 2 1/4" tall with a 28" chain that feeds through the top of the "V".

name: Cuff/Chain Bracelet
description:
Hand formed and polished 4" cuff with a faceted hammered texture with chain that measures 3" with 1" extension.

** Please specify which metal you would like when you check out!

name: Knuckle Ring
description:
One tiny faceted hammered ring that fit just below your first knuckle. Can also be worn as a pinky ring. 

The ring come in two sizes; 
Small - 2.5
Medium - 3.5

name: Black Crystal Quartz Ring
description: Raw, titanium (black) coated crystal, measuring approx 1" - 1 1/2" in a hammered, four prong setting with pointed claws on a faceted 14k gold fill hammered band.

name: 14k Rose Gold Horseshoe Studs
description: Handmade, hammered and polished 14k rose gold fill horseshoe charms on sterling silver studs and backings.

name: Little Raspberry Red Garnet Ring
description: Round, faceted raspberry colored garnet stone measuring approx 1/8", wrapped with 14k gold fill wire.

name: Sterling Silver "X" Necklace
description: Handmade, shaped and polished "X" pendant with a round hammered texture. "X" measures 1 1/2" wide x 2" tall with a 28" chain that feeds through the top of the "X".

name: 14k Gold Fill Herkimer Diamond Quartz Ring
description:
Raw, smokey, double terminated herkimer diamond quartz stone measuring approx 3/4", in a hammered, four prong setting with pointed claws on a faceted hammered band.

** Also available in Sterling Silver - please specify during check out!

name: Little Pearl Ring
description: Freshwater pearl measuring approx 1/4", wrapped with 14k gold fill wire.

name: Sterling Silver "U" Necklace
description: Handmade, shaped and polished "U" pendant with a flat hammered texture. "U" measures 3" wide x 1 1/2" tall with a 28" chain that feeds through the top of the "U".

name: Tear Bangle
description: Matte, brushed, hand filed finish that measures approx 3" wide.

name: Triangle Studs
description: Tiny brass triangle charms measuring 1/4"  on sterling silver posts.

name: Herkimer Diamond Quartz Ring
description: Double terminated, clear herkimer diamond quartz measuring approx 1/4", wrapped with 14k gold fill wire.  A herkimer diamond stone is a quartz, and some stones have more of a smokey texture with black flecks which give them a unique texture.

name: Hammered Feather Wrap Ring
description:
Perfect mix of feminine and bold statement jewelry. The band is hammered with two textures and is one size, but is adjustable. Each ring is one of a kind and comes in two types of metal: sterling silver and 14k gold fill. 

Please specify metal type when you check out!

name: Hammered Cuff
description: Handmade, organically shaped, cuff with a faceted hammered texture.  The cuff measures approx 4-4 1/2" and just under 1/8" wide. It is also adjustable, light and comfortable that looks great on it's own or with other bracelets.

name: Hammered Stacking Ring
description:
Faceted hammer texture, high polish finish, measuring approx 1.5mm thick. 

This style of ring is great for stacking or wearing alone.

name: Gold Brass Arrow Stud
description: Gold tone solid brass arrow charm on sterling silver posts and backings. Brass arrow measures approx 2".

name: Gem Studs
description:
3mm round faceted gemstones set in four prong settings with sterling silver posts and backings.  

Black Spinel - Pure black gemstone that sparkles like a black diamond.

Garnet - Beautiful red/pink stone that changes in the sunlight.

name: Tear Ring
description: Handmade, smooth, tear shaped ring with a high polish finish. Simple, yet edgy design that can be worn with the point up or down. Looks great alone or with other stacking rings!
